                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for separating heavy metal ions through membrane filtration, heavy metal ion separation membrane used by method and preparation method of heavy metal ion separation membrane",
                    "一种膜过滤分离重金属离子的方法及其所用重金属离子分离膜和制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the technical field of separation membranes, and particularly relates to a method for separating heavy metal ions through membrane filtration, a heavy metal ion separation membrane used by the method and a preparation method. The method comprises the following steps: (1) mixing a thermoplastic polymer material and epoxy resin in proportion, stirring after irradiation, dropwise adding an aromatic hydrocarbon solution, heating and stirring to prepare a carrier; (2) mixing imidazolium salt, a metal organic crystal and a pore-forming agent in proportion to prepare a membrane casting solution; and (3) uniformly coating two surfaces of a carrier with the membrane casting solution to prepare the composite separation membrane. A skeleton structure and holes are constructed through organic functional groups and metal organic crystals, heavy metal ions remaining in the hydrogen bromide preparation process are rapidly and efficiently separated, and the separation membrane obtains excellent ion separation selectivity through huge difference of different ions or molecules transmitting energy barriers through membrane holes."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于分离膜技术领域，特别涉及一种膜过滤分离重金属离子的方法及其所用重金属离子分离膜和制备方法。所述方法包括：（1）将热塑性高分子材料与环氧树脂按比例混合，辐照后搅拌，滴加芳香烃溶液，升温搅拌，制备载体；（2）将咪唑盐、金属有机晶体与造孔剂按比例混合，制备铸膜液；（3）将铸膜液均匀涂布在载体两面，制备复合分离膜。本发明通过有机官能团和金属有机晶体构建骨架结构和空穴，实现对溴化氢制备过程中残留的重金属离子快速、高效地分离，并通过不同离子或分子通过膜孔传输能垒的巨大差异，使得分离膜获得了优异的离子分离选择性。"
                }
            ]
